<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, wie ew dise
                                <expan>gege<ex>n</ex>wertig</expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> arm
                        lewte, <expan>czeig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> briefs, gesagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        wie daz sie Michel <expan>Pfragn<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er,</ex></expan> sein habe gen
                            <expan>Dietr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hasla umb ein gelt
                            <expan>awszgewonne<ex>n</ex></expan> und dafür
                            <expan>gesproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süllen, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>; und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                        edel <expan>wisse<ex>n,</ex></expan> daz die <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        selber nicht czü uns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sind,
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan> ein bote hat uns
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief geantwurt und wir
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
                        Michel <expan>Pfragn<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, darumb cze rede gesaczt und
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat uns
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz die <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        von <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> nichts
                                <expan>gesproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> noch die
                                <expan>awsgenome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und er hab sie auch dar umb nye
                                <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> wan im des kein notdurft wer und im
                                <expan>Dietr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hasla nichts cze nemen begert. <pb facs="#facs_485" id="242r"/>Dewcht
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> die <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz
                        sie <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> iht <expan>cze sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>het<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wöllen wir in oder iren
                                <expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor dez reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie czü
                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so derselb unser
                                <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist; und wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dinst
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> möht, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et Pauli.</ab>
